\s Kuchema kwomunhu ari panjodzi huru-huru
\d Rwiyo, Pisarema ravanakomana vaâ€‘ Kora; kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weMaharati
\s Reanoti. Rwiyo rweMashiri rwaHemani
\s muEzirahi.
\p
\v 88 I Jehovha, Mwari muponesi wangu,
\s Ndakachema masikati nousiku pamberi penyu;
\p
\v 2 Munyengetero wangu ngaupinde pamberi penyu;
\s Rerekerai nzeve yenyu munzwe kuchema kwangu;
\p
\v 3 Nokuti mweya wangu uzere namadambudziko,
\s Upenyu hwangu hwoswedera kuSheori.
\p
\v 4 Ndinoverengwa pamwechete navanoburukira kugomba;
\s Ndakafanana nomunhu anoshaiwa mubatsiri;
\p
\v 5 Ndakarashirwa pakati pavakafa, Savakaurawa vavete mubwiro, Vamusati mucharangarira; Vakagurwa paruoko rwenyu.
\p
\v 6 Makandiisa mugomba
\s rakadzika-dzika,
\s Panzvimbo dzine rima, makadzika kwazvo.
\p
\v 7 Hasha dzenyu dzinorema kwazvo
\s pamusoro pangu, Makanditambudza namafungu enyu
\s ose.
\p
\v 8 Makaisa vazikani vangu kure neni; Makandiita chinhu chinonyangadza kwavari;
\s Ndakapfigirwa, handigoni kubuda.
\p
\v 9 Ziso rangu ropera nemhaka yokutambudzika;
\s Ndakadana kwamuri, Jehovha,
\s zuva rimwe nerimwe, Ndakatambanudzira maoko angu
\s kwamuri.
\s lo Mungaitira vakafa zvinoshamisa here?
\p Ko vakaparara vangamuka vakakurumbidzai here?
\v 11 Hunyoro hwenyu hungaparidzwa
\s mubwiro here?
\s Kana kutendeka kwenyu
\s mukuparadza here?
\p
\v 12 Zvishamiso zvenyu zvingazikanwa murima here?
\s Nokururama kwenyu panyika yokukanganwa here?
\p
\v 13 Asi ndakachema kwamuri, Jehovha, Munyengetero wangu uchasvika pamberi penyu mangwanani.
\p
\v 14 Jehovha, munorashireiko mweya wangu?
\s Munovanzireiko chiso chenyu kwandiri?
\p
\v 15 Kubva pauduku hwangu ndakanga ndichitambudzwa ndichirwisofa; Kana ndichityiswa nemi
\s ndinoshaiwa mano.
\p
\v 16 Kutsamwa kwenyu kukuru kwakapfuura
\s napamusoro pangu;
\s Kutyisa kwenyu kwakandiparadza.
\p
\v 17 Zvakandikomberedza zuva rose semvura;
\s Zvakandipoteredza pamwechete.
\p
\v 18 Iye, anondida, neshamwari yangu,
\s -
\s makavaisa kure neni, Nomuzikani wangu ari murima.
